brazil treasuri to relea coff buy fund the treasuri depart is due to relea fund for the brazilian coff institut , ibc , to pay for the coff purcha from local produc , the ibc said in a statement . ibc product director orip gome said in the statement that payment would be made within the offici guarant price . the statement said the ibc is send a document to the nation monetari council ask the govern to set a budget for the purcha by the institut of up to five mln bag of coff until june 30. gome said in the statement there have been no problem in the concess of fund by the treasuri for payment of the coff deliv to the ibc wareh by the produc . he said produc have alreadi deliv 2.2 mln bag , of which 1.5 mln bag have been paid for . in the futur , accord to an agreement to be sign with the treasuri , the institut will no longer need to seek approv by the treasuri to seek the relea of addit fund to buy coff , the statement said .